OL,3,C'The sun will rise tomorrow': US man
OL,4,C'given second chance' after face
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FITV News' Graham Stothard reports on
OL,8,Fthe remarkable "life-giving" operation
OL,10,FWarning: this article contains details
OL,11,Fand images that some readers may find
OL,12,Fdistressing.
OL,14,FA US man says he's been give a "second
OL,15,Fchance" at life after undergoing a
OL,16,F"miracle" face transplant ten years
OL,17,Fafter he suffered catastrophic facial
OL,18,Finjuries.
