OL,7,FOver the past decade Derek Pfaff has
OL,8,Fundergone 58 reconstructive surgeries
OL,9,Fbut was still missing a nose, his
OL,10,Fupper and lower jaw, teeth, his
OL,11,Feyelids and part of his forehead bone.
OL,12,FHe was unable to chew or speak easily.
OL,14,F"There was still a lot of work that
OL,15,Fneeded to be done, and there was
OL,16,Freally nothing more that the hospital
OL,17,For facility could do for him," his
OL,18,Fmother, Lisa Pfaff, said.
