OL,7,FAt the time, she said, a doctor told
OL,8,Fher: "The only option for Derek is a
OL,9,Fface transplant."
OL,11,FPfaff, 30, is now one of just several
OL,12,Fdozen people in the world who have
OL,13,Fsuccessfully received a life-changing
OL,14,Fface transplant.
OL,16,FThe operation took a team of more than
OL,17,F80 over 50 hours to complete and his
OL,18,Fmother called it "just a miracle".
