OL,7,FA key part of the surgery was bringing
OL,8,Fa smile back to Mr Pfaff's face
OL,9,Fthrough building muscles around the
OL,10,Fmouth.
OL,12,F"You should see a smile on his face
OL,13,F(...) that part of the surgery is what
OL,14,Freally creates success," Dr Samir
OL,15,FMardini said. "It's not a lifesaving
OL,16,Fprocedure, but it's a life-giving
OL,17,Fprocedure".
OL,19,FDerek said that he "looked like a
OL,20,Fperson again" after his face transplant
