OL,7,FThey surgically removed a donor's face
OL,8,Fand implanted this tissue onto
OL,9,FDerek's. His reconstructed face is
OL,10,Fabout 85% donated, said Dr Mardini who
OL,11,Fled the surgery.
OL,13,FThe team had to do the surgery
OL,14,Fdigitally first, working out how they
OL,15,Fwould perform the surgery on a
OL,16,Fcomputer, before Derek went into the
OL,17,Foperating theatre. They printed a 3D
OL,18,Fmodel of the transplant ahead of time
OL,19,Fwhich they referred to during the
OL,20,Fsurgery.
