OL,7,F"He wasn't allowed to have a camera,
OL,8,Fhis phone, his iPad," Derek's mother
OL,9,FLisa said. "The mirror in the bathroom
OL,10,Fwas covered so he couldn't see
OL,11,Fhimself."
OL,13,FDerek's injuries were caused by a
OL,14,Ffailed suicide attempt when he was a
OL,15,F20-year-old student in March 2014.
OL,17,FExactly ten years after that fateful
OL,18,Fnight was when Derek was finally was
OL,19,Fable to see his new face for the first
OL,20,Ftime.
