OL,7,F"We turned a really sad, hard day into
OL,8,Fa really joyful experience for Derek,
OL,9,Fand it was just a miracle ` a miracle
OL,10,Ffor him to see himself," his mother
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FWhile at the hospital, Derek looked in
OL,14,Fa mirror. He said that he "looked like
OL,15,Fa person again" and that he had been
OL,16,Fgiven "a second chance."
OL,18,FHe can now express emotions on his
OL,19,Fface: joy, laughter, sadness and
OL,20,Fdisappointment. He can speak much more
OL,21,Fclearly and easily.
