OL,7,FHe works out twice a week, trains with
OL,8,Fa speech therapist and takes
OL,9,Fimmunosuppressive drugs to reduce the
OL,10,Frisk of transplant rejection, which
OL,11,Fhappens when a transplant recipient's
OL,12,Fimmune system attacks the donor's
OL,13,Forgan or tissue. He will continue to
OL,14,Ftake these medications for the rest of
OL,15,Fhis life.
OL,17,FOverall, Derek said, he is "doing
OL,18,Fwell." He is excited about his future
OL,19,Fand now wants to "help others" by
OL,20,Fraising suicide awareness.
