OL,7,F"The sun will rise tomorrow," he said.
OL,8,F"You just have to stay positive, no
OL,9,Fmatter what the situation is. Look
OL,10,Fpast the down."
OL,12,F"We're so proud of (him) and
OL,13,Feverything that he has overcame over
OL,14,Fthe last 10 years with a fighting
OL,15,Fspirit and staying positive," his
OL,16,Fmother said.
